title: 2019 Week 6 Preview
itunes:title: 2019 Week 6 Preview
description:
Ricky's hotel room filled with heroes - Dan Hanzus, Marc Sessler, Chris Wesseling and Gregg Rosenthal preview each game of week 6 including the "QB" showdown between the Texans and the Chiefs and the most anticipated game of the week... Dolphins and Redskins. Sam Darnold is back which could make the Jets- Cowboys game more interesting and Ricky falls asleep during Dan's lock. MY MIND.
